you have a lot to think about.

4
00:00:09,460 --> 00:00:12,190
Here are some of the considerations
you should keep in mind.

5
00:00:12,190 --> 00:00:15,795
First, is your idea a painkiller or
a vitamin?

6
00:00:15,795 --> 00:00:19,210
Painkillers address an obvious and
functional need for users.

7
00:00:19,210 --> 00:00:23,420
While vitamins address users emotional
needs and are really nice to have.

8
