say the simplest explanation

22
00:01:07,690 --> 00:01:10,240
is usually the right or truthful one.

23
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:12,690
And this should also be
true of your product.

24
00:01:12,690 --> 00:01:14,800
Users should be able to
describe the product and

25
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:18,170
its benefits to other
potential users easily.

26
